Voice-Activated Emergency Trigger
The system detects distress keywords like “help” and activates instantly without requiring any manual interaction.
 
 Real-Time location Sharing
Automatically captures and transmits the user’s live location at the moment of distress.

 Automatic Audio Evidence Recording
Initiates audio recording immediately after activation to preserve critical evidence.

 Centralized Alert Dashboard
Displays incoming alerts with user details, location, and status, simulating a real-time response system.

 Multi-Trigger Detection Logic
Supports activation through repeated keywords or sudden sound intensity changes, improving reliability.

 Hands-Free Operation
Designed to function even when the user cannot physically access their device.
